spec_data.Name: perl-LWP-Authen-Wsse
spec_data.Description:
LWP::Authen::Wsse allows LWP to authenticate against servers that are
using the X-WSSE authentication scheme, as required by the Atom
Authentication API.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 12:43:52 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Library for enabling X-WSSE authentication in LWP
